{"tid":494810,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[港狗盲反]又一了一趟深圳，把個人感覺包括電子支付分享大家","createTime":"2017-12-10T05:32:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-14T03:50:42.000Z","uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"89402fa3f204ded75ef39421eeca170851f2e489","tid":494810,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T05:32:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img3.laibafile.cn/p/m/287591959.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg3.laibafile.cn%2Fp%2Fm%2F287591959.jpg&h=2022734e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n昨天又去了深圳一趟，身處在這感覺上還是那樣很不舒服，可能香港整體環境比較設施完善基礎設施齊備！對比之下令我感到身處深圳很不舒服！<br />\n<br />\n　　香港無論食品及任何貨品有更多選擇，很多用品更輕易買到，各式各樣的餐廳林林種種！<br />\n<br />\n　　從這角度看，開始了解為什麼大陸的網購及支付系統為什麼開始那麼多盛行，因為基礎設施實在太不完善！<br />\n<br />\n　　另外在乘車方面我叫了架滴滴，已提前約車但亦要等幾分鐘，當走出路面太太一揮手叫了架的士，罵了一句（你好無聊啊）後來我取消柯打了！上了車同的士司機聊了一會，他說現在滴滴亦没有優惠反而加價了，很多位置他們更不能進入反而要乘客遷就去找所叫的車！<br />\n<br />\n　　晚上去了太陽廣場頂樓吃噸飯，又嘗試用桌上的二維條碼掃下叫餐，怎料太太已叫好所有菜我手機還未登入系統！<br />\n<br />\n　　每個消費都用了微信或支付寶付款，感覺很不方便，要用幾個動作才能付款，對比香港的支付太不爽了！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bbs.tianya.cn/post-208-98358-1.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbbs.tianya.cn%2Fpost-208-98358-1.shtml&d=ePCWnjtSfoUi8ES%2FkCpDSxv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=767de2c9\" target=\"_blank\">http://bbs.tianya.cn/post-208-98358-1.shtml</a>"},{"pid":"450caa6dc7728a4ba6240489728544176002cf51","tid":494810,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T05:33:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"559933464b407aede8edef1985191be446f4c84a","tid":494810,"uid":22736,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T06:00:28.000Z","msg":"好撚假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27bcf88c1d26ce633a62f4964bfb38496a4fbba1","tid":494810,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T06:07:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好撚假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f284fd77a170fa6e15ff2ddf44900c7269f6f586","tid":494810,"uid":108090,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T06:12:46.000Z","msg":"唔講其他<br />\n你嗌個侍應黎落單<br />\n同你用部電話禁兩禁落單<br />\n明顯後者有效率好多，既唔洗侍應寫，又冇左人手限制"},{"pid":"f1c8f9023bbb84ca3efc9b07f3057e91f973c073","tid":494810,"uid":25086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T03:50:42.000Z","msg":"落order 同電子支付有咩關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}